                    p.case-text.case-platform-text Omlet is an open messaging system that lets users own their data in the repository of their choice. Based on Omlet, we create private communication between doctors, patients, and caregivers, as well as data transfer between IoTs.
                    a(class='btn case-btn case-btn-omlet') Download Omlet
