                    h3.case-platform-text-title.case-platform-text.case-platform-title-sabrina Sabrina
                    p.case-text.case-platform-text Sabrina is an opensource messaging assistance platform built on Omlet. As a chat bot in the Omlet Chat app, Sabrina uses natural language to communicate with users, recommends and executes IoT rules, and can even provide emotional support through the chat interface.
